SIMPLE: ruffler
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ruffler
<hw>Ruf"fler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
ruffles; a swaggerer; a bully; a ruffian.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Assaults, if not murders, done at his own doors by that crew of
<qex>rufflers</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which ruffles; specifically, a sewing machine
attachment for making ruffles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rufigallic</ent>⟦br⟧
